window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The beastkin have evened the score. Now it's time to reclaim their world.</b></p> <p>Jake and his wives have fought against the evil invaders to exhaustion, and the war is escalating to its conclusion. The beastkin have been empowered, and allies have been gathered.</p> <p>But greater rifts threaten to release powerful enemies, and champions of evil gods have arrived. The vicious naga prepare their ambush, and the terrible undead legions roam. Then, there is the difficult dungeon raid, which could send their budding kingdom crumbling down, should they fail.</p> <p>Will their guild be victorious against Tartarus, crowning Jake king of Highlands? Or will all the beastkin be slain, their efforts for nothing?</p>"; 
